ðŸ’¼ Requirements:
Every Notification must have:

A title, message, and recipient

A method to compose the notification (common)

A method to send the notification (channel-specific)

Each delivery channel:

Has its own logic to send (e.g., SMTP, SMS gateway, push API)

May support optional features like:

Tracking (e.g., delivery reports)

Scheduled delivery

You should be able to easily add new notification types or delivery methods in the future.

